name: $identifier
desc: Returns: The identifier for the stratifier used to coordinate the reported data back to this stratifier.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The identifier for the stratifier used to coordinate the reported data back to this stratifier.

name: $criteria
desc: Returns: The criteria for the stratifier. This must be the name of an expression defined within a referenced library.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The criteria for the stratifier. This must be the name of an expression defined within a referenced library.

name: $path
desc: Returns: The path to an element that defines the stratifier, specified as a valid FHIR resource path.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The path to an element that defines the stratifier, specified as a valid FHIR resource path.
